  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Researchers are trying to determine if providing education on proper disposal of unused
      opioid medications to the orthopedic patient undergoing a planned hip or knee total joint
      replacement will increase the percentage of patients who properly dispose of unused opioids.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
